8️⃣ Key Differences
Feature	TCP	UDP
Reliability	Guaranteed	Not guaranteed
Packet order	Maintained	Not maintained
Speed	Slower	Faster
Connection	Required	Connectionless
Use case	Data integrity	Real-time communication
9️⃣ How This Connects to Earlier Topics
Technology	Protocol
HTTP	TCP
WebSocket	TCP
WebRTC	UDP
Video streaming	UDP
REST APIs	TCP
